✔ Sustainable Materials – Growing demand for recycled/renewable NVH products
✔ Asia-Pacific Growth – Booming automotive production in India and Southeast Asia
Challenges
❌ Material Cost Volatility – Petroleum-based material price fluctuations
❌ Thinner Material Requirements – Balancing noise reduction with lightweighting
❌ Adoption of Active Noise Cancellation – Potential threat to passive NVH materials
